In the beginning, there was a vision to create a cloud platform that would empower organizations to innovate and transform their businesses. And so, Microsoft Azure was born, with a wide range of services and technologies that allow businesses to build, deploy, and manage applications in the cloud. As an Azure Architect, you are responsible for designing and implementing these solutions, ensuring that they meet the needs of your organization.
This Bible is a comprehensive guide to Azure Architect Technologies, covering everything you need to know to be successful in this role.
